<item>
            <title>[LU-4129] Successive calls to libcfs_debug_dumplog() can result in large number of log files and errors</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4129</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Successive calls to libcfs_debug_dumplog() can occur with no delay between calls and can generate a very large number of log files and error messages like this over and over:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;2009-08-01 00:45:59&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;c2-0c1s1n0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;LustreError: dumping log to /tmp/lustre-log.1249105560.4266&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;2009-08-01 00:45:59&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;c2-0c1s1n0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;LustreError: can&apos;t open /tmp/lustre-log.1249105560.4266 file: err -17&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;2009-08-01 00:45:59&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;c2-0c1s1n0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;LustreError: dumping log to /tmp/lustre-log.1249105560.4266&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;2009-08-01 00:45:59&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;c2-0c1s1n0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;LustreError: can&apos;t open /tmp/lustre-log.1249105560.4266 file: err -17&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This proposed patch will make debug log file name more unique.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>lustre/libcfs</environment>
